{% doc %}
  @prompt
    帮我生成一个适用于 Shopify Dawn 主题的横向滑动卡片模块（类似分类推荐 carousel）。
    
    ### 一、布局要求（PC端）
    
    - 顶部左侧为模块标题（如：Start with Top Picks）
    - 右上角有左右切换按钮（箭头）
    - 下方为横向滑动卡片列表（carousel）
    - 模块整体居中显示
    - 左右两侧边距：50px
    - 模块支持自定义上下边距（padding）
    - 模块内部卡片之间有间距（如16px-24px）
    - 卡片为固定宽度，右侧可露出部分下一张卡片（增强滑动感）
    - 桌面端单位使用 px
    - 图片采用 cover 填充模式（object-fit: cover）
    - 卡片圆角（如12px）
    
    ---
    
    ### 二、卡片与功能要求
    
    每个卡片（block）支持：
    
    - 整张图片可点击（可设置链接）
    - 图片上方有标签（类似按钮样式）：
      - 显示标题（如：Q3M8 Cam >）
      - 位于图片左上角
      - 白色背景 + 圆角
    
    图片内容支持叠加：
    
    - 标题 + 描述 + 按钮（可选显示）
    - 可单独设置：
      - 字体大小
      - 字体颜色
    - 内容位置可配置（左上 / 左下 / 居中）
    - 移动端标题、描述、按钮间距更紧凑
    
    交互效果：
    
    - hover 卡片轻微放大或阴影效果
    - 支持鼠标拖动滑动
    - 支持按钮点击切换
    
    ---
    
    ### 三、响应式要求
    
    - PC端：横向滑动，一行多个卡片
    - 平板：适当减少卡片数量和间距
    - 移动端：
      - 支持手指滑动
      - 卡片变小
      - 内容适配（字体缩小，间距更紧凑）
    
    ---
    
    ### 四、后台可配置（Shopify schema）
    
    - 模块标题
    - 上下边距（padding top / bottom）
    - 卡片列表（blocks）：
      - 图片
      - 链接
      - 标题
      - 描述
      - 按钮文字
      - 按钮链接
    - 内容是否显示开关
    - 内容位置选择（左 / 中 / 右）
    
    ---
    
    ### 五、性能优化（重点必须满足）
    
    - 代码结构简洁，避免冗余 DOM
    - 不引入任何额外 JS 或第三方库
    - 使用 Dawn 原生 slider 或原生 JS
    - 图片优化：
      - 使用 loading="lazy"
      - 使用 Shopify image_url 控制尺寸
    - 避免 CLS（布局偏移）：
      - 提前设置图片容器宽高比（aspect-ratio）
    - 减少 DOM 层级，结构扁平化
    - 不影响页面整体加载速度
    
    ---
    
    ### 六、技术要求
    
    - 使用 Liquid + HTML + CSS
    - 完全兼容 Dawn 主题
    - 使用 Dawn 原生 slider 结构（如 slider、slider__slide）
    - 不影响原主题样式（避免全局污染）
    - 使用 scoped / 局部 class 命名
    - 不修改全局 CSS
    
    ---
    
    ### 输出要求
    
    - 输出完整 Shopify section 代码（Liquid + schema + CSS）
    - 可直接复制到 section 文件中使用, 桌面控制的单位为px，图片展示铺满，卡片的高度按图片自适应
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: calc(100% - 100px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 50px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
  }

  .ai-carousel-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_bg_color }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.arrow_border_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.arrow_hover_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.3;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.arrow_color }};
  }

  .ai-carousel-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    cursor: grab;
  }

  .ai-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}.dragging {
    cursor: grabbing;
    transition: none;
  }

  .ai-carousel-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 {{ block.settings.card_width }}px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .ai-carousel-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-carousel-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1.33;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-carousel-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-carousel-tag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    left: 16px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.tag_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.tag_text_color }};
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.tag_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.tag_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}.position-top-left {
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}.position-bottom-left {
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}.position-center {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.content_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.content_title_color }};
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.content_desc_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.content_desc_color }};
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.content_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.content_button_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.content_button_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.content_button_size }}px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-carousel-content-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.content_button_hover_bg }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: calc(100% - 60px);
      padding: 0 30px;
    }

    .ai-carousel-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc({{ block.settings.card_width }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .ai-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
    }

    .ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: 100%;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-carousel-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc({{ block.settings.card_width }}px * 0.65);
    }

    .ai-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: calc({{ block.settings.card_gap }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .ai-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.75);
    }

    .ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 16px;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .ai-carousel-content-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.content_title_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-carousel-content-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.content_desc_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-carousel-content-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.content_button_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-carousel-tag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      top: 12px;
      left: 12px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.tag_font_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-carousel-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 8px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<carousel-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-carousel-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
      <div class="ai-carousel-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <h2 class="ai-carousel-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
        <div class="ai-carousel-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <button class="ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-carousel-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Previous slide">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M15 18L9 12L15 6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button class="ai-carousel-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-carousel-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Next slide">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M9 18L15 12L9 6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-carousel-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for i in (1..6) %}
          {% liquid
            assign image_key = 'card_image_' | append: i
            assign link_key = 'card_link_' | append: i
            assign tag_key = 'card_tag_' | append: i
            assign show_tag_key = 'show_tag_' | append: i
            assign show_content_key = 'show_content_' | append: i
            assign content_position_key = 'content_position_' | append: i
            assign content_title_key = 'content_title_' | append: i
            assign content_desc_key = 'content_desc_' | append: i
            assign show_button_key = 'show_button_' | append: i
            assign button_text_key = 'button_text_' | append: i

            assign card_image = block.settings[image_key]
            assign card_link = block.settings[link_key]
            assign card_tag = block.settings[tag_key]
            assign show_tag = block.settings[show_tag_key]
            assign show_content = block.settings[show_content_key]
            assign content_position = block.settings[content_position_key]
            assign content_title = block.settings[content_title_key]
            assign content_desc = block.settings[content_desc_key]
            assign show_button = block.settings[show_button_key]
            assign button_text = block.settings[button_text_key]
          %}

          <div class="ai-carousel-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <a 
              href="{% if card_link != blank %}{{ card_link }}{% else %}#{% endif %}" 
              class="ai-carousel-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              <div class="ai-carousel-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if card_image %}
                  <img
                    src="{{ card_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                    alt="{{ card_image.alt | escape }}"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="{{ card_image.width }}"
                    height="{{ card_image.height }}"
                    class="ai-carousel-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  >
                {% else %}
                  <div class="ai-carousel-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if show_tag and card_tag != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-carousel-tag-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ card_tag }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if show_content %}
                  <div class="ai-carousel-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} position-{{ content_position }}">
                    {% if content_title != blank %}
                      <h3 class="ai-carousel-content-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ content_title }}</h3>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if content_desc != blank %}
                      <p class="ai-carousel-content-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ content_desc }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if show_button and button_text != blank %}
                      <span class="ai-carousel-content-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ button_text }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</carousel-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
(function() {
  class CarouselSlider{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
    constructor() {
      super();
      this.track = this.querySelector('.ai-carousel-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.prevBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-carousel-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.nextBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-carousel-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.slides = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-carousel-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
      this.currentIndex = 0;
      this.isDragging = false;
      this.startPos = 0;
      this.currentTranslate = 0;
      this.prevTranslate = 0;
    }

    connectedCallback() {
      if (!this.track || this.slides.length === 0) return;

      this.setupEventListeners();
      this.updateButtons();
    }

    setupEventListeners() {
      if (this.prevBtn) {
        this.prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.prev());
      }
      if (this.nextBtn) {
        this.nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.next());
      }

      this.track.addEventListener('mousedown', this.dragStart.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('touchstart', this.dragStart.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('mouseup', this.dragEnd.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('touchend', this.dragEnd.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('mouseleave', this.dragEnd.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('mousemove', this.drag.bind(this));
      this.track.addEventListener('touchmove', this.drag.bind(this));
    }

    getPositionX(event) {
      return event.type.includes('mouse') ? event.pageX : event.touches[0].clientX;
    }

    dragStart(event) {
      this.isDragging = true;
      this.startPos = this.getPositionX(event);
      this.track.classList.add('dragging');
    }

    drag(event) {
      if (!this.isDragging) return;
      const currentPosition = this.getPositionX(event);
      this.currentTranslate = this.prevTranslate + currentPosition - this.startPos;
    }

    dragEnd() {
      if (!this.isDragging) return;
      this.isDragging = false;
      this.track.classList.remove('dragging');

      const movedBy = this.currentTranslate - this.prevTranslate;
      
      if (movedBy < -50 && this.currentIndex < this.slides.length - 1) {
        this.next();
      } else if (movedBy > 50 && this.currentIndex > 0) {
        this.prev();
      } else {
        this.setPositionByIndex();
      }
    }

    prev() {
      if (this.currentIndex > 0) {
        this.currentIndex--;
        this.setPositionByIndex();
      }
    }

    next() {
      if (this.currentIndex < this.slides.length - 1) {
        this.currentIndex++;
        this.setPositionByIndex();
      }
    }

    setPositionByIndex() {
      const slideWidth = this.slides[0].offsetWidth;
      const gap = {{ block.settings.card_gap }};
      const offset = this.currentIndex * (slideWidth + gap);
      
      this.currentTranslate = -offset;
      this.prevTranslate = this.currentTranslate;
      this.track.style.transform = `translateX(${this.currentTranslate}px)`;
      
      this.updateButtons();
    }

    updateButtons() {
      if (this.prevBtn) {
        this.prevBtn.disabled = this.currentIndex === 0;
      }
      if (this.nextBtn) {
        this.nextBtn.disabled = this.currentIndex >= this.slides.length - 1;
      }
    }
  }

  customElements.define('carousel-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}', CarouselSlider{{ ai_gen_id }});
})();
</script>

